msgstr "The celebration grew from the ancient festival of Samhain and the later observance of All Hallows’ Eve, blending seasonal rites with remembrance of the dead."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/autumn-equinox.tsx:126
msgid "The colour change in autumn leaves isn’t new pigment appearing — it’s the green chlorophyll withdrawing, revealing yellows and oranges that were there all along."
msgstr "The colour change in autumn leaves isn’t new pigment appearing — it’s the green chlorophyll withdrawing, revealing yellows and oranges that were there all along."

