msgstr "The Geminids are one of the strongest and most reliable meteor showers of the year, appearing each December with frequent, bright meteors."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/eid-al-adha.tsx:71
msgid "The holiday commemorates the story of Ibrahim and his willingness to sacrifice in obedience to God."
msgstr "The holiday commemorates the story of Ibrahim and his willingness to sacrifice in obedience to God."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/valentines.tsx:71
