msgstr "The holiday we recognise today grew from early Christian tradition, layered over much older European midwinter customs tied to light, renewal, and community."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/leonids.tsx:83
msgid "The Leonids are a November meteor shower, named for their radiant in the constellation Leo."
msgstr "The Leonids are a November meteor shower, named for their radiant in the constellation Leo."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/leonids.tsx:99
