#~ msgstr "The shower frequently delivers swift, luminous streaks that carve clean lines across the night."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/lyrids.tsx:104
msgid "The shower originates from Comet Thatcher, which returns to the inner solar system roughly every four hundred and fifteen years."
msgstr "The shower originates from Comet Thatcher, which returns to the inner solar system roughly every four hundred and fifteen years."

