msgstr "The tradition grows from Indigenous Mexican beliefs about death and the afterlife, later blending with Catholic observances of All Saints’ and All Souls’ Days."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/christmas.tsx:102
msgid "The tradition of a decorated Christmas tree only became widespread in the English-speaking world after an 1848 illustration of Queen Victoria and Prince Albert’s tree was published — and went viral, by Victorian standards."
msgstr "The tradition of a decorated Christmas tree only became widespread in the English-speaking world after an 1848 illustration of Queen Victoria and Prince Albert’s tree was published — and went viral, by Victorian standards."

#: src/features/seasonal-events/events/halloween.tsx:101
